    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You are wielding a Mourneblade in your hand</p>\n<hr />\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Your Mourneblade is imbued with the power to bend through reality, allowing it to seemingly lengthen, bend and cut through space farther than it should.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"mso-tab-count:1\">            </span>When you cast this spell, you Strike against up to 3 enemy creatures within the area with your Mourneblade, at your current multi-attack penalty. You gain multi-attack penalty at the end of your Strikes. At the end of this spell, your Mourneblade shatters.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Heightened</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">(5<sup>th</sup>): Your weapon lengthens, allowing you to choose a 15ft. diagonal cone or 15ft. line or a 10 ft. emanation.</span></p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">Heightened</span></strong><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\">(8<sup>th</sup>): You can target any number of enemy creatures within the spell’s area.</span></p>"
